Ba ADF bakufi na bitumba na ba FARDC na Mamove na Beni






Mapinga ya FARDC ezali kosenga na bavandi na Mamove bakende na zamba te mpo kobengana ba ADF esili naino te.
"Ba ADF bakufi ebele, tomemi bibembe na bango minei. Bibwele nyionso bayibaki tozuwi yango mpe tozongiseli bakolona na yango. Mino nyonso bazuwaki na kati ya lopitalo, tozongisa yango. Tokamati mpe bibundeli na bango: PKM moko, AK 47 minei, ba roquettes mpe biloko ebele maye to botoli na bamaboko ya banguna, " ebakisi major Hazukay.